<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
    <head>
        <title>CSS Test: Inline replaced elements and auto specified for margin left and right</title>
        <link rel="author" title="Microsoft" href="http://www.microsoft.com/" />
        <link rel="help" href="http://www.w3.org/TR/CSS21/visudet.html#the-width-property" />
        <meta name="flags" content="" />
        <meta name="assert" content="Computed value of 'auto' for 'margin-left' or margin-right' on inline replaced elements becomes a used value of '0'." />
        <style type="text/css">
            .c1
            {
                background: green;
                border: solid 1px black;
            }
            div
            {
                width: 600px; /* Prevent line wrapping */
            }
            textarea
            {
                margin-left: auto;
                margin-right: 10px;
                border: solid 1px black;
                overflow: hidden;
                width: 100px;
                background-color: blue;
            }
            p
            {
                width: 50%;
            }
            body
            {
                margin: 0;
            }
        </style>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div>
            <span class="c1">Filler Text</span><textarea rows="1" cols="1">Filler Text</textarea><span class="c1">Filler Text</span>
        </div>
        <p>Test passes if no white space is seen between the left green box and the blue box. A space is seen between the right green box and the blue box.</p>
    </body>
</html>